enhanced_by.reason: Both methods require the generation of digits based on birth date and gender, which can be reused for setting up the test environment.
The pickGender method is used to determine the gender, which is a prerequisite for the get method.
The generateValid method is invoked before get to ensure the environment is set up correctly with valid ID number generation criteria.
The getControlDigit method is used to calculate the control digit, which is a part of the ID number generation process in the get method.
